	Portugal (4-4-2): 1-Eduardo; 3-Paulo Ferreira, 2-Bruno Alves, 6-Ricardo Carvalho, 23-Fabio Coentrao, 15-Pepe, 16-Raul Meireles, 19-Tiago, 7-Cristiano Ronaldo, 11-Simao Sabrosa, 9-Liedson         
